           move      74                   to   v-pos                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ripristino immagine video                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       box-msg-err-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Box per messaggio di errore esteso, su due righe          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       box-msg-e02-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio immagine video                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Video in Off                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
