      *                          * Titolo                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      72                   to   v-car                  .
           move      10                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "                           A T T E N Z I O N E    
      -              "                      "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Prima riga                          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
